<title>USA: Fortune Petroleum Corp Q1 net loss widens.</title>
<headline>Fortune Petroleum Corp Q1 net loss widens.</headline>
<dateline>HOUSTON 1997-05-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>1997			1996</p>
<p> Shr loss		   $0.06     loss	 $0.02</p>
